{"tid":930940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會班「議員」去美國遊說 小心被美國政府拘捕","createTime":"2018-12-06T16:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T13:34:41.000Z","uid":14918,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ef901c5ec7ec0056fd7fe127e2118eafbab28d10","tid":930940,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"now新聞台： 周浩鼎低調訪問美國 唱好香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/930833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/930833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咩話？去見美國政界、官員遊說佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國嚴厲執行《外國代理人登記法》 為外國政府活動的人必須登記<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部加強了鮮為人知的《外國代理人登記法》的執行力度，<span style=\"color: red;\">一直隱秘活動的外國遊說人員和施加影響的人因此必須披露他們的活動。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1938年為了對抗納粹的宣傳而頒布的這項法律，要求公關專業人士、律師事務所和其他在美國為外國政府工作的人向司法部登記，並且每6個月申報一次他們的活動。過去由於執法鬆弛和監督不力，許多遊說人士對這項法律置之不理。但是，特別檢察官在涉俄調查期間援引這項法律起訴違法人員，從而改變了執法的現狀。<br />\n<br />\n短篇轉載<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/foreign-agent-20180918/4577891.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fforeign-agent-20180918%2F4577891.html&d=mH1e2yiDRGEDVvCN%2Bholn8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=95f1d91a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/foreign-agent-20180918/4577891.html</a>"},{"pid":"f8242bdb901ecd518a6c68bfd3b80f8053e0198e","tid":930940,"uid":25468,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"以中國人身份去美國做說客但又事先唔登記就拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f8c5268192a2a1c25b915bb7ac7d69ab1e4477","tid":930940,"uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"阿董熟美國地方<br />\n叫埋佢陪埋去包唔會蕩失路"},{"pid":"38b9745afcf0b